The paper is about automated program repair, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category. The use of ensemble learning and convolutional neural machine translation (NMT) models suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The fact that the technique is applied to multiple programming languages (Java, C++, Python, and JavaScript) suggests a focus on programming languages (cs.PL) and natural language processing (cs.CL) as well.
